'''1931年富蘊地震'''發生於8月11日21時18分<ref>{{cite web |url=http://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/eqarchives/year/mag8/magnitude8_1900_date.php |title=Magnitude 8 and Greater Earthquakes Since 1900 |publisher=Earthquake.usgs.gov |date= |accessdate=2011-10-22 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160414014457/http://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/eqarchives/year/mag8/magnitude8_1900_date.php |archivedate=2016-04-14 }}</ref>，[[震央|震央]]位於中國[[新疆省_(中華民國)|新疆省]][[富蕴县|富蕴县]]，震級達里氏8.0級<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www-lgit.obs.ujf-grenoble.fr/users/vergnolm/Documents/Pollitzetal_JGR_03.pdf |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2010-07-24 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110721023048/http://www-lgit.obs.ujf-grenoble.fr/users/vergnolm/Documents/Pollitzetal_JGR_03.pdf |archivedate=2011-07-21 }}</ref>，並有171公里長地表破裂<ref name="ujf-grenoble1"/>，水平位移最大為14公尺<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ieexa.cas.cn/kxcb/kpdt/200806/t20080604_1662984.html |title=地震知识-中国科学院地球环境研究所 |publisher=Ieexa.cas.cn |date=2008-06-04 |accessdate=2011-10-22 |archive-date=2020-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107191240/http://www.ieexa.cas.cn/kxcb/kpdt/200806/t20080604_1662984.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

可可托海-二台斷裂帶引起這次地震<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.springerlink.com/content/3646j58908071017/ |title=Science in China Series D: Earth Sciences, Volume 40, Number 2 |publisher=SpringerLink |date= |accessdate=2011-10-22 }}{{Dead link|date=2020年3月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>，每年滑移率為4±2毫米<ref>http://www.paper.edu.cn/index.php/default/journal/downCount/journal-1005-2321(2003)S1-0132-10{{Dead link}}</ref>。富蘊地震造成10,000人死亡。

